            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showVignette",
                    "vignetteName": "MourningKyro.png",
                    "crossFadeTime": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.fade",
                    "scope": "FadeIn",
                    "fadeTime": 2,
                    "fadeTime2": "0.5",
                    "wait": true,
                    "fadeDown": 1,
                    "fadeColorR": 0,
                    "fadeColorG": 0,
                    "fadeColorB": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.wait",
                    "waitForSeconds": "1"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b72220f1-d712-453b-8fbe-0a1a2faee15c",
                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I have to admit, I'm going to miss the twerp. He was polite. He went out of his way to find cool things for me to buy from him. Kinda made me feel special.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "38562c35-29ca-4502-8a7c-be00f80f9a1c",
                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I could have saved him... if only I started searching for him a little sooner... He looked so sad lying on the cold Catacombs stone. I felt like I betrayed him.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "84062e42-9a52-4116-8ba8-74d31309916b",
                    "actorId": "98ea49aa-86cf-4fa9-9bd5-6aa2fe7c809d",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I should have hunted for him. I vas sure he vould be found by someone. I did not think he vould die.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "3cd357a3-247a-4126-8d53-a9694539bccc",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b307681c-5d51-4a37-96cc-9ebefede2f46",
                            "text": "Say Something Polite",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "ceb9dd6e-e4cc-4644-b17a-1330f2438cf8",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "50",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "bb6d8ea3-796b-403c-ac88-fa2222f6bc53",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "We may not have saved Joel, but at least we tried. It's not our fault that we couldn't help him.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "922b465d-b44a-41fb-a5cf-fb4f345e10a8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Joel was always eager-to-please and friendly. He was a really good thief... and he'd have been a great Rogue if Sosi didn't have him on a leash. ",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true,
                            "notes": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ace95cd8-db43-47b1-82dc-7b5d30ea0a42",
                            "text": "Say Something Clever",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "8df20600-9586-4abd-9f0d-b65d84fa6f10",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "50",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7334a041-eecf-4800-b08b-dd7a991cf6da",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Joel was always in Sosi's shadow. It was odd how Sosi had no idea what had happened to Joel. I guess we'll never really know what happened to Joel, but if anyone should feel guilty about Joel - it should be Sosi.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true,
                            "notes": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "dd43fb74-c89b-4977-8ca5-42a896a93cdf",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "73d8b739-d6db-47c1-83d5-c8a1540bb30c",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "50",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "45df458a-8a77-4177-b8fc-85604fe5d66b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Poor Joel - he has more friends now than when he was alive. We'll forget he was a sneaky, lying thief who stole from Katie and tried to get me kicked out of school. We'll just miss that he ran the best black market in the school.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
